[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1173238","time":"2016-8-8 21:39","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"(✨️VIP 8✨️)","message":"并不能在自制字体内调整与其它字体字符之间的字距。字距没法跨字体的。<br>不过otf字体有个合字特性，也许可以单独制作“T♁”“L☽”两个合字…不过我现在在外不便制作字体，没法测试行不行。我想想谁能帮你…<br><br>话说这☽符是模仿金文月字吗。<br><img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/7016afdcjw1f6l250ltosj20dm0j875r.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1173252","time":"2016-8-8 22:14","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"不是的，是模仿外国手写占星术符号。<br>游戏有可能不能支持字体的高级特性，程序员没有用到 iOS 自身的字体引擎。我先学一下。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/08/893.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1173667","time":"2016-8-11 11:58","userId":"linkzero","userName":"Link/Zero","userSign":"","message":"不需要用连字，如果干脆要做一个合成字体的话，用 kerning 就能解决楼主的问题了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#2-3","id":"1173691","time":"2016-8-11 14:36","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Link/Zero</span> 说: 不需要用连字，如果干脆要做一个合成字体的话，用 kerning 就能解决楼主的问题了</q></div>但是有人告诉我不能在自制字体内调整与字体 Avenir 字符之间的 kerning，我也确实没查到方法。如果你的意思是让我在字体中加上英文整个代替 Avenir 字体的话，那样工作量就很大，游戏就做不完了。<br>而且我毕竟是外行，不了解英文 kerning 有什么讲究，所以没有自制英文字体的打算。<br>感觉没有什么捷径可走……"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/24/272459.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1173249","time":"2016-8-8 22:04","userId":"272459","userName":"自动姬","userSign":"","message":"<a href=\"/user/295353\" class=\"l\">@belleve</a>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1173255","time":"2016-8-8 22:19","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"惊了，belleve也在bgm？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/61/66129.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1173277","time":"2016-8-9 09:04","userId":"grubstreet","userName":"小寒","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: 惊了，belleve也在bgm？</q></div>这种技术问题，还是问belleve这种搞字体工程的比较靠谱，我就不掺合了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1173286","time":"2016-8-9 11:49","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">小寒</span> 说: 这种技术问题，还是问belleve这种搞字体工程的比较靠谱，我就不掺合了</q></div>我觉得字体运用也是门学问，制作字体的人有时会局限于字体内部的和谐，不一定跟设计师一样精通多种字体联合运用。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/61/66129.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1173290","time":"2016-8-9 12:47","userId":"grubstreet","userName":"小寒","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: 我觉得字体运用也是门学问，制作字体的人有时会局限于字体内部的和谐，不一定跟设计师一样精通多种字体联合运用。</q></div>本来就是不同的分工，我是说题主这个事还是技术人员来解答比较靠谱。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/08/893.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1173666","time":"2016-8-11 11:55","userId":"linkzero","userName":"Link/Zero","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: 我觉得字体运用也是门学问，制作字体的人有时会局限于字体内部的和谐，不一定跟设计师一样精通多种字体联合运用。</q></div>这个问题和字体运用没什么关系吧，基本上就是个技术问题。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#3-6","id":"1173674","time":"2016-8-11 12:32","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Link/Zero</span> 说: 这个问题和字体运用没什么关系吧，基本上就是个技术问题。</q></div>呃，我当时在想，这可能不是字体制作技术，而是排版技术中关于多种字体混用的技术。我印象中小寒懂这方面。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1173254","time":"2016-8-8 22:17","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"(✨️VIP 8✨️)","message":"有意思，♁符在不同字体里显示得不一样，有的是圈加号，有的是倒过来的♀。<br><br>在bgm我认识这些人（按ID字母排序）：<br><a href=\"/user/buernia\" class=\"l\">@奈白不弍</a> ，爱好字体设计，有自制字体；<br><a href=\"/user/doream\" class=\"l\">@Doream</a> ，<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/group/fonts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">字體硏究小组</a>创建者；<br><a href=\"/user/drizztvii\" class=\"l\">@DrizztVII</a> ，汉仪字体设计师；<br><a href=\"/user/grubstreet\" class=\"l\">@小寒</a> ，字体运用方面；<br><a href=\"/user/linkzero\" class=\"l\">@Link/Zero</a> ，爱好字体排印；<br><a href=\"/user/yukirock\" class=\"l\">@チャド·ロー</a> ，制作过字体比较工具；<br>…还有没有我遗漏的人？应该可以帮到，除非你的问题确实是无解的。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1173261","time":"2016-8-8 22:34","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Earth_symbol.svg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Earth_symbol.svg</a> 维基百科以圆形田字为准，所以我也这么画。<br><br>居然有这么多人！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#4-2","id":"1173275","time":"2016-8-9 08:12","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"D7居然去汉仪了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/18/11854.jpg","floor":"#4-3","id":"1173754","time":"2016-8-11 23:00","userId":"drizztvii","userName":"DrizztVII","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烈之斩</span> 说: D7居然去汉仪了</q></div>呀，小烈好久不见"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/38/3811.jpg","floor":"#4-4","id":"1174062","time":"2016-8-14 08:40","userId":"kane","userName":"Kane","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">DrizztVII</span> 说: 呀，小烈好久不见</q></div>干！"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#4-5","id":"1174063","time":"2016-8-14 08:54","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Earth_symbol.svg 维基百科以圆形田字为准，所以我也这么画。<br><br>居然有这么多人！</q></div>圆田…确实更符合地球的符号。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#4-6","id":"1174065","time":"2016-8-14 08:55","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Kane</span> 说: 干！</q></div>？你也认识？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/38/3811.jpg","floor":"#4-7","id":"1174067","time":"2016-8-14 09:36","userId":"kane","userName":"Kane","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">林卯</span> 说: ？你也认识？</q></div>来bgm以前就"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#4-8","id":"1174068","time":"2016-8-14 09:38","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Kane</span> 说:</q></div>基本不同的道路呢。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/30/123081.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1173276","time":"2016-8-9 08:55","userId":"doream","userName":"Doream","userSign":"(夜海全书)","message":"不同字体间的字间距应该用排版属性控制，比如css的 letter-spacing","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1173410","time":"2016-8-9 21:13","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"游戏引擎并不是 HTML5，也许不能类比。不过单纯在网页上，怎样写 letter-spacing 达到图下方的效果？我看了 W3School 的相关教程没发现我需要的。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/90/189040.jpg","floor":"#5-2","id":"1173438","time":"2016-8-9 22:56","userId":"prevails","userName":"Donuts","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 游戏引擎并不是 HTML5，也许不能类比。不过单纯在网页上，怎样写 letter-spacing 达到图下方的效果？我看了 W3School 的相关教程没发现我需要的。</q></div>写负值"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-3","id":"1173557","time":"2016-8-10 14:33","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Donuts.</span> 说: 写负值</q></div>有些组合不能是负值，而且这个符号字体会有上千个符号。或者是我理解得不对？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/30/123081.jpg","floor":"#5-4","id":"1173558","time":"2016-8-10 14:34","userId":"doream","userName":"Doream","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Donuts.</span> 说: 写负值</q></div>正值也行，写小一点"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/90/189040.jpg","floor":"#5-5","id":"1173561","time":"2016-8-10 14:37","userId":"prevails","userName":"Donuts","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 有些组合不能是负值，而且这个符号字体会有上千个符号。或者是我理解得不对？</q></div>我的意思是用行内元素, 比如span, 调整特定的一两个字母的 letter-spacing, 其它的保持正常<br><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre><span style=\"letter-spacing: -8px;\">T</span>♁rra</pre></div>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-6","id":"1173562","time":"2016-8-10 14:38","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Doream</span> 说: 正值也行，写小一点</q></div>万一玩家改为 Te♁♁a ，我是说，我没查到单独调整某一对的 CSS 语法。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-7","id":"1173568","time":"2016-8-10 15:01","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Donuts.</span> 说: 我的意思是用行内元素, 比如span, 调整特定的一两个字母的 letter-spacing, 其它的保持正常</q></div>这样显示可以解决，也可以复制，但我想，放到游戏中玩家就不能简单地编辑了。看来并没有捷径可走。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/18/90/189040.jpg","floor":"#5-8","id":"1173571","time":"2016-8-10 15:07","userId":"prevails","userName":"Donuts","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 这样显示可以解决，也可以复制，但我想，放到游戏中玩家就不能简单地编辑了。看来并没有捷径可走。</q></div>还要能编辑吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"> 我在想玩家怎么打出那两个字母"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/30/123081.jpg","floor":"#5-9","id":"1173579","time":"2016-8-10 16:17","userId":"doream","userName":"Doream","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 这样显示可以解决，也可以复制，但我想，放到游戏中玩家就不能简单地编辑了。看来并没有捷径可走。</q></div>我还以为是固定显示呢，原来你想要随机显示啊"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/08/893.jpg","floor":"#5-10","id":"1173664","time":"2016-8-11 11:51","userId":"linkzero","userName":"Link/Zero","userSign":"","message":"这个应该用字体自身的 kerning 来解决，而不是调 tracking（也就是 CSS 中的 letter-spacing）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/30/123081.jpg","floor":"#5-11","id":"1173685","time":"2016-8-11 14:15","userId":"doream","userName":"Doream","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Link/Zero</span> 说: 这个应该用字体自身的 kerning 来解决，而不是调 tracking（也就是 CSS 中的 letter-spacing）</q></div>不知道LZ的引擎支不支持不同字体间kerning"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-12","id":"1173692","time":"2016-8-11 14:38","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Doream</span> 说: 不知道LZ的引擎支不支持不同字体间kerning</q></div>我有查过，好像都没有不同字体间 kerning 的概念啊。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-13","id":"1173698","time":"2016-8-11 15:03","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Donuts.</span> 说: 还要能编辑吗 我在想玩家怎么打出那两个字母</q></div>我想，届时玩家不需要打出，可以复制粘贴的。<br>其实这是游戏中初始地区的2个星球的名称。作为宇航游戏，可能会有上亿星球，我们事先给所有恒星都赋予了随机命名，然后行星名跟随恒星，卫星跟随行星……为此我将制作一个有上千“外星”字符的字体，在一个范围内不会出现有恒星重名的情况。<br>当然，必须要做到能让玩家改为有意义的名称，这就要支持编辑功能：除了输入还有剪切复制粘贴。“外星”字符也可以复制粘贴，因为都是真正存在于 Unicode 的。而且我觉得和英文中文搭配都很和谐：<br><img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/large/006xHUHGgw1f6ptbh0agyj30db06u407.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/30/123081.jpg","floor":"#5-14","id":"1173700","time":"2016-8-11 15:23","userId":"doream","userName":"Doream","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 我有查过，好像都没有不同字体间 kerning 的概念啊。</q></div>那这样就直接写kerning就好了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-15","id":"1173726","time":"2016-8-11 20:23","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Doream</span> 说: 那这样就直接写kerning就好了</q></div>怎样直接写？我还没有明白你的意思。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/30/123081.jpg","floor":"#5-16","id":"1173945","time":"2016-8-12 23:47","userId":"doream","userName":"Doream","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 怎样直接写？我还没有明白你的意思。</q></div>在字体编辑软件里写啊<br>belleve这样的人就跟在行，不过他在知乎里面活跃"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-17","id":"1174041","time":"2016-8-13 19:10","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Doream</span> 说: 在字体编辑软件里写啊<br>belleve这样的人就跟在行，不过他在知乎里面活跃</q></div>但之前写过，没有不同字体间 kerning 的概念，换句话说字体编辑软件里本来就没处可写，因为字体不支持。所以我还没有明白你的意思。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#5-18","id":"1202546","time":"2017-1-8 12:10","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Link/Zero</span> 说: 这个应该用字体自身的 kerning 来解决，而不是调 tracking（也就是 CSS 中的 letter-spacing）</q></div>我决定自制一个原创字体（<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/group/topic/341921\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">展示页</a>），追加 Avenir 所有字符，终于可以 kerning 了。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/54/95483.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1173281","time":"2016-8-9 10:33","userId":"howegulf","userName":"CMK","userSign":"(No Music, No Life)","message":"调一下 Kerning 就行了，字体混用的话得参考下文档，Core Text 还是 CTFont 记不清了<br><br><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/72d7aee5jw1f6naksn0w8j20ts0npgpe.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">哈，不用苹果那套 SDK 我也没招</span><br><br>理论上可以用底层 API 将调整好的字体画到图像里，然后给你的游戏引擎调用，不过那样的话一开始就做成图片不就好了，还是这样工作量太大 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/06.gif\" smileid=\"45\" alt=\"(bgm29)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1173406","time":"2016-8-9 21:03","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"#2所说“字距没法跨字体”有道理吗？像我的字体演示网页那样，T 与 ♁ 分别是用2个字体呈现的。<br>游戏里出现的这段字符玩家应该是可以编辑的，恐怕不能图片化，不过我也不了解游戏引擎具体怎样运作。刚才问了程序员，说引擎不是 core text, 不过必要时也可支持 kerning。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/54/95483.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1173433","time":"2016-8-9 22:44","userId":"howegulf","userName":"CMK","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: #2所说“字距没法跨字体”有道理吗？像我的字体演示网页那样，T 与 ♁ 分别是用2个字体呈现的。<br>游戏里出现的这段字符玩家应该是可以编辑的，恐怕不能图片化，不过我也不了解游戏引擎具体怎样运作。刚才问了...</q></div>游戏引擎方面我也不太懂。控制字距可以从字体本身和排版引擎两方面着手，<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">不过</span>想要在字体文件内搞定这个问题的确不可以。<br><br>Cocoa Touch 支持混排字体和字体样式等特性的调整，粒度也可以精细控制。至于其他平台，那得让懂行的人来看了。我只玩过 OpenGL，渲染文字简直烦 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/14.gif\" smileid=\"53\" alt=\"(bgm37)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#6-3","id":"1173559","time":"2016-8-10 14:34","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">CMK</span> 说: 游戏引擎方面我也不太懂。控制字距可以从字体本身和排版引擎两方面着手，不过想要在字体文件内搞定这个问题的确不可以。<br><br>Cocoa Touch 支持混排字体和字体样式等特性的调整，粒度也可以精细控制。至于...</q></div>要是能像网页那样简单就好啦。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/08/893.jpg","floor":"#6-4","id":"1173665","time":"2016-8-11 11:53","userId":"linkzero","userName":"Link/Zero","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: #2所说“字距没法跨字体”有道理吗？像我的字体演示网页那样，T 与 ♁ 分别是用2个字体呈现的。<br>游戏里出现的这段字符玩家应该是可以编辑的，恐怕不能图片化，不过我也不了解游戏引擎具体怎样运作。刚才问了...</q></div>其实如果不考虑版权问题的话，替换掉 Avenir 里的相关字符（不动原有 kerning，或是根据替换的字符稍作调整）是最简单的做法。<br><br>考虑到版权问题，最好找一款风格近似的开源字体来替代掉 Avenir 进行上述更改。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#6-5","id":"1173699","time":"2016-8-11 15:16","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Link/Zero</span> 说: 其实如果不考虑版权问题的话，替换掉 Avenir 里的相关字符（不动原有 kerning，或是根据替换的字符稍作调整）是最简单的做法。<br><br>考虑到版权问题，最好找一款风格近似的开源字体来替代掉 Aven...</q></div>不考虑版权也许问题可以简单解决，但这要发布到苹果商店的，这是苹果的经典字体，很难蒙混过关。<br>而找到质量相当于 Avenir 的开源字体也不容易，调整到满意可能相当于从头自制字体的劳动，而自制字体对我的难处我已经在上面作了回复。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/18/11854.jpg","floor":"#6-6","id":"1173757","time":"2016-8-11 23:11","userId":"drizztvii","userName":"DrizztVII","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 不考虑版权也许问题可以简单解决，但这要发布到苹果商店的，这是苹果的经典字体，很难蒙混过关。<br>而找到质量相当于 Avenir 的开源字体也不容易，调整到满意可能相当于从头自制字体的劳动，而自制字体对我的...</q></div>唔，游戏引擎的解释完全不懂呢……不过你可以看看这里面哪个有免费或者便宜的商业授权的<br><a href=\"http://typecache.com/font-clusters/11/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://typecache.com/font-clusters/11/</a><br><a href=\"http://typecache.com/font-clusters/14/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://typecache.com/font-clusters/14/</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#6-7","id":"1173767","time":"2016-8-11 23:34","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">DrizztVII</span> 说: 唔，游戏引擎的解释完全不懂呢……不过你可以看看这里面哪个有免费或者便宜的商业授权的<br>http://typecache.com/font-clusters/11/<br>http://typecache.co...</q></div>把风格合适的都看了一遍……果然合适和免费不能并存啊。要正圆形的“o”又不要十字架形的“t”，单是这个要求就排除了不少字体。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/08/893.jpg","floor":"#6-8","id":"1173911","time":"2016-8-12 18:35","userId":"linkzero","userName":"Link/Zero","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">DrizztVII</span> 说: 唔，游戏引擎的解释完全不懂呢……不过你可以看看这里面哪个有免费或者便宜的商业授权的<br>http://typecache.com/font-clusters/11/<br>http://typecache.co...</q></div>买商业授权也不能解决吧，涉及到修改字体文件本身的话。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/08/893.jpg","floor":"#6-9","id":"1173912","time":"2016-8-12 18:36","userId":"linkzero","userName":"Link/Zero","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">钛白</span> 说: 把风格合适的都看了一遍……果然合适和免费不能并存啊。要正圆形的“o”又不要十字架形的“t”，单是这个要求就排除了不少字体。</q></div>如果对字重要求不大的话，可以试试 Montserrat."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#6-10","id":"1173930","time":"2016-8-12 21:17","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Link/Zero</span> 说: 如果对字重要求不大的话，可以试试 Montserrat.</q></div>对字重的要求比较苛刻。我的自制字体基本是为了与“Avenir Light”和“苹方-简 细体”搭配的，正如 CSS 写的那样。<br><img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/large/006xHUHGgw1f6ptbh0agyj30db06u407.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>不过程序员说，如果大多数人看不出来，为了消除复杂性，标题这个可以延后解决。<br>明年的话我打算按我的风格复刻一遍“Avenir Light”，将来也许会制作简单的中文字体。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#6-11","id":"1202548","time":"2017-1-8 12:12","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">DrizztVII</span> 说: 唔，游戏引擎的解释完全不懂呢……不过你可以看看这里面哪个有免费或者便宜的商业授权的<br>http://typecache.com/font-clusters/11/<br>http://typecache.co...</q></div>我自制了一个原创字体（<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/group/topic/341921\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">展示页</a>），准备追加 Avenir 所有字符，终于可以 kerning 了。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/25/202532.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1173740","time":"2016-8-11 21:43","userId":"buernia","userName":"奈白不弍","userSign":"(我追番少，你可别骗我。)","message":"被@了，提点想法吧：<br>看这个效果图，两个符号的高度与小写字母不太一样。可以把符号高度降低，与字母（视觉上）齐平，可以更好地与字母搭配。<br><br>其它符号的设计最好也像这样与西文字体的各基准线对齐。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1173762","time":"2016-8-11 23:20","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"我已经发现了。但符号一开始就画在1000×618点的黄金比框中，所有线条都对齐到点，笔画宽度全都一致，天文符号底端与小写英文对齐，尺寸已经精确下来没法改了。<br><br>不过我说服自己这一千个符号并非英文而是另一套外星文明的文字体系。目前可以保证与苹方中文混合对齐的效果。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1174282","time":"2016-8-15 19:57","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"(参与i游戏开发设计中。昵称是种颜料。 ...)","message":"可能技术上暂时还做不到，我的这个想法暂时就搁置吧。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/43/14382.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1175405","time":"2016-8-22 04:38","userId":"laoism","userName":"林卯","userSign":"(✨️VIP 8✨️)","message":"今天看Rewrite想起来，这单词应该是Terra吧？那么下面的是Luna？拉丁文？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/02/290256.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1175479","time":"2016-8-22 20:02","userId":"taiceart","userName":"钛白","userSign":"","message":"没错，在游戏里象征地球和月球。"}]}]